# 5. Environment Configuration

System configuration is managed through a `.env` file.

Example configuration:

POSTGRES_DB=ai_assistant\
POSTGRES_USER=ai_user\
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=strongpassword

DATABASE_URL=postgresql://ai_user:strongpassword@postgres:5432/ai_assistant

REDIS_URL=redis://redis:6379/0

TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=`<bot_token>`{=html}

OPENAI_API_KEY=`<optional>`{=html}\
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=`<optional>`{=html}\
KIMI_API_KEY=`<optional>`{=html}

STORAGE_INPUT_DIR=/storage/input\
STORAGE_OUTPUT_DIR=/storage/output

BACKEND_HOST=0.0.0.0\
BACKEND_PORT=8000

